00:12:25.500 --> 00:12:28.370 align:middle line:84%
And I have to laugh because,
yeah, I do know that,

00:12:28.370 --> 00:12:30.640 align:middle line:84%
but how are we going to do
that when the power to do

00:12:30.640 --> 00:12:33.850 align:middle line:84%
this is in the
hands of our enemy?

00:12:33.850 --> 00:12:38.540 align:middle line:84%
So the next part of
that question is, how?

00:12:38.540 --> 00:12:44.310 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that
the answer to that

00:12:44.310 --> 00:12:48.310 align:middle line:84%
question-- I might approach it
from a hilarious point of view

00:12:48.310 --> 00:12:51.120 align:middle line:90%
and say, well, very slowly.

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:52.010 align:middle line:90%
And that is true.

00:12:52.010 --> 00:12:55.580 align:middle line:84%
It can't all be done at once,
but that's not the real issue.

00:12:55.580 --> 00:12:56.960 align:middle line:90%
How do we do it?

00:12:56.960 --> 00:13:03.500 align:middle line:84%
We have to do it with that
dreaded thing called power.

00:13:03.500 --> 00:13:10.660 align:middle line:84%
One of my greatest mistakes,
I think, in my early awareness

00:13:10.660 --> 00:13:12.460 align:middle line:84%
of this movement
is that I thought

00:13:12.460 --> 00:13:16.910 align:middle line:84%
power, especially governmental
power, was the problem.

00:13:16.910 --> 00:13:19.210 align:middle line:84%
Power of the state
was the problem,

00:13:19.210 --> 00:13:25.322 align:middle line:84%
and so I would speak eloquently,
I hope, against power--

00:13:25.322 --> 00:13:27.280 align:middle line:84%
that we've got to avoid
concentration of power,

00:13:27.280 --> 00:13:30.610 align:middle line:84%
and we've got to work to
eliminate power, reduce power

00:13:30.610 --> 00:13:34.810 align:middle line:84%
everywhere we find it to allow
individuals to have the freedom

00:13:34.810 --> 00:13:39.100 align:middle line:84%
to do what they want
without being coerced.

00:13:39.100 --> 00:13:43.000 align:middle line:84%
And then one morning
I woke up, literally.

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:45.630 align:middle line:84%
I guess I'd been thinking
about it or dreaming about it,

00:13:45.630 --> 00:13:47.010 align:middle line:90%
and I remember I woke up.

00:13:47.010 --> 00:13:49.300 align:middle line:84%
I don't remember if I
actually sat up or not,

00:13:49.300 --> 00:13:54.600 align:middle line:84%
but I felt like I did, and
I said, oh, we reject power.

00:13:54.600 --> 00:13:57.200 align:middle line:90%
We lose.

00:13:57.200 --> 00:14:00.200 align:middle line:84%
That was a hard thing
for me to grapple with,

00:14:00.200 --> 00:14:05.840 align:middle line:84%
because I'd always been thinking
that power was the problem,

00:14:05.840 --> 00:14:07.740 align:middle line:84%
and then I finally
realized that power

00:14:07.740 --> 00:14:11.300 align:middle line:84%
is not the problem anymore
than guns are the problem.

00:14:11.300 --> 00:14:12.970 align:middle line:90%
Guns don't kill people.

00:14:12.970 --> 00:14:16.920 align:middle line:84%
People kill people with
guns, and the only thing

00:14:16.920 --> 00:14:21.150 align:middle line:84%
more dangerous than having
guns is not having guns.

00:14:21.150 --> 00:14:25.180 align:middle line:84%
And so I made the analogy
that the question with guns

00:14:25.180 --> 00:14:32.840 align:middle line:84%
is not guns themselves, but the
conditions of gun ownership,

00:14:32.840 --> 00:14:38.170 align:middle line:84%
and the freedom to have guns
versus regimenting society

00:14:38.170 --> 00:14:40.150 align:middle line:90%
to eliminate guns, and so forth.

00:14:40.150 --> 00:14:42.750 align:middle line:84%
I recognize that if we
got rid of all guns,

00:14:42.750 --> 00:14:45.160 align:middle line:84%
and it was only in the
hands of criminals, well,

00:14:45.160 --> 00:14:47.550 align:middle line:84%
we'd know that the
criminal rules society.

00:14:47.550 --> 00:14:48.790 align:middle line:90%
So I made the analogy.

00:14:48.790 --> 00:14:50.540 align:middle line:84%
I said, OK, power
is not the problem,

00:14:50.540 --> 00:14:53.750 align:middle line:84%
because if we don't
have the power

00:14:53.750 --> 00:14:58.440 align:middle line:84%
to dislodge our enemy from these
positions of power that he has,

00:14:58.440 --> 00:15:01.920 align:middle line:84%
he's going to stay
in those positions.

00:15:01.920 --> 00:15:06.780 align:middle line:84%
You cannot overcome power
without equal or greater power,

00:15:06.780 --> 00:15:09.410 align:middle line:84%
and that was a
frightening thought to me,

00:15:09.410 --> 00:15:13.520 align:middle line:84%
but it has mellowed well, and
I realize now after quite a few

00:15:13.520 --> 00:15:16.790 align:middle line:84%
years of living with that
thought that it is true.

00:15:16.790 --> 00:15:18.900 align:middle line:84%
The question then
is, well, how do

00:15:18.900 --> 00:15:22.520 align:middle line:84%
we prevent-- if we strive
for power ourselves,

00:15:22.520 --> 00:15:26.872 align:middle line:84%
we must reach out and acquire
the very political power,

00:15:26.872 --> 00:15:28.580 align:middle line:84%
and the power in the
media and everywhere

00:15:28.580 --> 00:15:31.310 align:middle line:84%
else-- the very power that
our opponents now have

00:15:31.310 --> 00:15:34.870 align:middle line:90%
if we want to succeed.

00:15:34.870 --> 00:15:38.300 align:middle line:84%
That being the case,
how can we do that?

00:15:38.300 --> 00:15:41.710 align:middle line:84%
And assuming we succeed,
how can we be sure

00:15:41.710 --> 00:15:44.420 align:middle line:84%
that we ourselves now that we're
in control of this power don't

00:15:44.420 --> 00:15:48.420 align:middle line:84%
become just as corrupt and evil
as the people we're opposing?

00:15:48.420 --> 00:15:52.194 align:middle line:84%
And therein lies the
answer to your question.

00:15:52.194 --> 00:15:54.110 align:middle line:84%
Can it be done, first
of all, is the question,

00:15:54.110 --> 00:15:56.860 align:middle line:84%
and I am very firmly
convinced that it

00:15:56.860 --> 00:16:00.000 align:middle line:84%
can be done if we go
about it intelligently.

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:03.370 align:middle line:84%
And then the question is,
well, how do we bring it about?

00:16:03.370 --> 00:16:07.760 align:middle line:84%
It can be done if we're very
clear on what our goals are.

00:16:07.760 --> 00:16:11.710 align:middle line:84%
If everybody enlisted in this
movement has a very clear

00:16:11.710 --> 00:16:15.350 align:middle line:84%
mental picture of what
we're trying to achieve,

00:16:15.350 --> 00:16:18.880 align:middle line:84%
if we have a creed, for
example-- this we believe--

00:16:18.880 --> 00:16:22.390 align:middle line:84%
and we really are
all on the same page,

00:16:22.390 --> 00:16:25.190 align:middle line:84%
and we agree to a certain
statement of principles,

00:16:25.190 --> 00:16:28.940 align:middle line:84%
and one of those principles is
that we cannot and must never

00:16:28.940 --> 00:16:34.280 align:middle line:84%
use political power or the
legalized force of coercion

00:16:34.280 --> 00:16:38.930 align:middle line:84%
to deny any person their freedom
unless it's to protect life,

00:16:38.930 --> 00:16:40.370 align:middle line:90%
liberty, and property.

00:16:40.370 --> 00:16:42.540 align:middle line:84%
If we are clear on
that, that those

00:16:42.540 --> 00:16:46.240 align:middle line:84%
are the limits of coercion,
of legalized coercion,

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:51.040 align:middle line:84%
then the risk of fraud and
corruption is greatly reduced.

00:16:51.040 --> 00:16:53.510 align:middle line:84%
Never completely
